A married man with kids has been keeping a secret mobile phone which he uses to stay in touch with other women in his life. This woman was stunned when she discovered a secret telephone which has the contacts of as many as 14 women whom her husband has slept with. He didn’t only sleep with them, he also made note about his s*x with them. This has been happening possibly for a long time under her nose and she was shocked she never got to know. She wrote her story to a relationship adviser and blogger, Joro Olumofin as she seeks advice.  Read her story below: Source